-align: justify;\">T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: Stoke 1-2 Tottenham<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Stoke vs Tottenham:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Stoke: Diouf (57\u2019)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\nTottenham: Eriksen (52\u2019 & 63\u2019)<br>\r\n<h2>Video highlights tr\u1eadn Stoke vs Tottenham:</h2>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265760\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/04/07/highlight-stoke-vs-tottenham-vong-33-nha.mp4&autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham t\u1ef1 tin h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Britannia v\u00e0 ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Stoke, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1edbi 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng Spurs kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n l\u00e9p v\u1ebf so v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean ph\u1ea7n, c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Christian Eriksen r\u1ed3i Son Heung-min \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, trong khi ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Harry Kane d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n. 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Stoke v\u00e0 Tottenham tr\u1edf v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1edbi hai con s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f2n tr\u0129nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eriksen\" title=\"Eriksen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/tong-hop-stoke-12-tottenham-vong-33-premier-league-201718.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn Stoke vs Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n m\u1edf m\u00e0n hi\u1ec7p hai kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 bao so v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm r\u00e3i c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00ec b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u1ec9 sau 7 ph\u00fat, khi Dele Alli ph\u00e1 b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c xu\u1ed1ng khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Stoke trong th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai theo k\u00e8m, sau \u0111\u00f3 tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Eriksen \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Stoke b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 5 ph\u00fat. T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hugo Lloris v\u1edbi pha ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Shaqiri, Diouf d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1, \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y khi c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 5 ph\u00fat sau, Spurs t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n v\u00e0 Harry Kane ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Stoke t\u1eeb pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a Eriksen. Tuy nhi\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng theo c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt c\u1ee7a trang ch\u1ee7 Premier League, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi Stoke kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho Tottenham. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 2-1 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 Spurs ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u00e2y ch\u1eafc m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong top 4 Premier League.</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn Stoke vs Tottenham:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p>Stoke (4-5-1): Butland \u2013 Johnson, Martins Indi, Shawcross, Pieters \u2013 Badou, Allen, Ramadan, Shaqiri, Bauer \u2013 Diouf <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Tottenham (4-2-3-1): Lloris \u2013 Aurier, Sanchez, Vertonghen, Rose \u2013 Wanyama, Dembele \u2013 Eriksen, Dele Alli, Son \u2013 Kane<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn Stoke vs Tottenham:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/11830038/013100\">Stoke vs Tottenham</span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"884","checkdouble":"183739"},{"date":"21:18 07/04","title":"Everton vs Liverpool: M\u00e0n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/everton-vs-liverpool-man-chay-da-khong-te-truoc-dai-chien.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold