lor:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ch\u1eb3ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i \u0103n thua \u0111\u1ee7 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a, v\u00e0 Klopp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u1eefa Everton vs Liverpool.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, trong \u0111\u00f3 2/3 m\u0169i \u0111inh ba kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, m\u1ed9t Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nanh vu\u1ed1t \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chia \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Everton. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Jurgen Klopp ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Everton vs Liverpool, b\u1edfi n\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>Sau khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng oanh li\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Champions League</span>, Liverpool \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 4 CLB m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian qu\u00e1 d\u00e0i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. V\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao khi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a The Kop \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton vs Liverpool c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n nhau 0-0\" title=\"Everton vs Liverpool M\u00e0n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/live.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton vs Liverpool c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n nhau 0-0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Ings &ndash; Dominic Solanke, hay \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Nathaniel Clyne, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y sau khi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u00ecn chung, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng (Clyne th\u00ec c\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a ch\u1eb3ng ai trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ebfm hoi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. D\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh (Wijnaldum &ndash; Henderson &ndash; Milner), Liverpool-kh\u00f4ng-Salah thi\u1ebfu h\u1eb3n nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn derby Merseyside \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mong ch\u1edd, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft d\u1ed3n b\u00f3ng cho Sadio Mane v\u00e0 h\u1ebft. 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o, trong khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n, hay ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u01a1 ra b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t bu\u1ed3n t\u1ebb khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e3y nh\u00ecn Danny Ings, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trung b\u00ecnh 1 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng&hellip; 1 l\u1ea7n, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 ch\u00fat n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh anh \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool. Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e1y quay h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed7i khi x\u00f4 x\u00e1t v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Everton, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Anfield.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Ings trong tr\u1eadn Everton vs Liverpool\" title=\"Danny Ings trong tr\u1eadn Everton vs Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/ings.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Ings kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra ch\u00fat \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t g\u1ecdi t\u00ean ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 25 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i, Ings ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p, loay hoay v\u00e0 tung \u0111\u1ebfn 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, ch\u1eb3ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng ph\u00f3 m\u1eb7c s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, thay v\u00ec t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, \u0111\u1ec3 cho Van Dijk. S\u00fat ph\u1ea1t, c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 cho Van Dijk. V\u00e0 khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh khi ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng h\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean ngang v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u00e2u gi\u1edd, ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Klopp c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u1edd \u01a1. Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 gi\u1eadn d\u1eef hay ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m, ch\u1ec9 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng v\u00e0 ph\u1edbt l\u1edd m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao The Kop ch\u1ec9 mong ch\u1edd ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Everton mu\u1ed1n &ldquo;\u0103n thua \u0111\u1ee7&rdquo; trong kho\u1ea3ng 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. T\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n h\u1ebft sang Etihad, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao, \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c m\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng Arnold, Firmino v\u00e0 Chamberlain \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. Nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool</span> \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n Chamberlain, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua Clyne c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp khong qua coi trong tran dau Everton vs Liverpool\" title=\"Klopp kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 coi tr\u1ecdng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Everton vs Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 coi tr\u1ecdng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Everton vs Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n1 \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong tr\u1eadn Everton vs Liverpool gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Klopp d\u1eadm ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng. H\u1ecd \u0111ang k\u00e9m Man United 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 2 tr\u1eadn. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, The Kop ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 l\u00e0m g\u00ec, khi h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 an to\u00e0n trong Top 4.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Etihad v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, Jurgen Klopp r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch toan t\u00ednh v\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f9ng l\u00e0 derby, v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch &quot;\u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3&quot; c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh. Gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi: <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Man-City-1471.html\" target=\"_blank\">Pep Guardiola</span> s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Everton vs Liverpool 0-0<br>\r\n</strong> <span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/11830266/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Everton 0-0 Liverpool<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265747\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/07/highlight-everton-vs-liverpool-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n</span>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-everton-00-liverpool-vong-33-premier-league-201718-326-183738.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/tong-hop-everton-00-liverpool-vong-33-premier-league-201718.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-everton-00-liverpool-vong-33-premier-league-201718-326-183738.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Everton 0-0 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 33 Premier League 2017/18)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"883","checkdouble":"183746"},{"date":"22:28 07/04","title":"Chelsea quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng v\u00ec huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 c\u1ed1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2013/12/ray-wilkins-20131210173851.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-ser