 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 g\u00ec.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea quyet thang vi huyen thoai Ray Wilkins qua doi hinh anh\" title=\"Chelsea quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng v\u00ec huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ray Wilkins qua \u0111\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2013/12/ray-wilkins-20131210173851.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea Ray Wilkins qua \u0111\u1eddi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 61</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2u \u0111au bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec c\u00e1i ch\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Ray Wilkins b\u1eb1ng Stamford Bridge, n\u01a1i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f9i \u00e1o s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i b\u1edfi c\u00e1c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u00e0m tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd d\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 HLV c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 theo l\u1eddi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cesar-azpilicueta-7-trieu-bang-thong-minh-nhat-chelsea-tung-chi-172-168986.html\">Cesar Azplicueta</span>, chuy\u1ec7n Ray Wilkins qua \u0111\u1eddi c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m West Ham v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb1m tri \u00e2n huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi tri \u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Ray Wilkins v\u00ec nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho Chelsea. Thay m\u1eb7t CLB, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng xin g\u1eedi l\u1eddi chia bu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ebfn gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u00f4ng \u1ea5y trong th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u00d4ng \u1ea5y m\u00e3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau m\u1ebfn \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u00e0ng ph\u00e1o tay m\u1eb7c ni\u1ec7m s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ee7. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thay l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/ray-wilkins-cuoc-doi-qua-nhung-buc-anh-389-183585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/ray-wilkins-cuoc-doi-qua-nhung-buc-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/ray-wilkins-cuoc-doi-qua-nhung-buc-anh-389-183585.html\">Ray Wilkins: Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi qua nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh</span><br>\r\nRay Wilkins, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u1eeba m\u1edbi ra \u0111i sau m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n tr\u1ee5y tim v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ecd 61 tu\u1ed5i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng khi c\u00f2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nGia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"882","checkdouble":"183747"},{"date":"22:51 07/04","title":"Pep Guardiola khen sao MU \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/pep-guardiola-khen-sao-mu-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:hover{color:#