eafn kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9ng nh\u00e2n cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m \u1ed3n \u00e0o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd \u00edt nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng thua \u1edf trong tr\u1eadn derby Man City vs MU tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch Etihad nh\u01b0 hai l\u1ea7n vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Derby Man City vs MU Guardiola khen Lukaku dang cap the gioi hinh anh\" title=\"Derby Man City vs MU Guardiola khen Lukaku \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/pep-guardiola-khen-sao-mu-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Pep Guardiola khen ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Romelu Lukaku\u00a0\u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby Man City vs MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf c\u0169ng s\u1ebd mang hy v\u1ecdng tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n ng\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng quang c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ed3i sinh c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Romelu Lukaku. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 HLV Pep Guardiola v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 khen ng\u1ee3i anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby Man City vs MU:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c24 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 100 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, m\u1ed9t m\u1ed1i hi\u1ec3m h\u1ecda th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 d\u00e0nh cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i v\u00e0 tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t Man City ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eddi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Everton cho b\u1ea1n t\u00f4i Ronald Koeman. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xung quanh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cRomelu Lukaku \u0111\u00edch th\u1ecb l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\nGia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"881","checkdouble":"183748"},{"date":"22:47 07/04","title":"\"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0m ph\u1ea3n, bu\u1ed9c Conte ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/7/cau-thu-chelsea-dang-lam-phan-buoc-conte-phai-ra-di.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-wei