   </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Leboeuf cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea ph\u1ea3n Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-quyet-thang-vi-huyen-thoai-qua-co-172-183747.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea</span> \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t Premier League \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17 v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua top 4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 2 t\u0103m t\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t b\u1ed7ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ea1. V\u00e0 b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y Mourinho kh\u1ecfi gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea l\u00e0 Leboeuf tin r\u1eb1ng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111ang l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Conte.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1c C\u0110V v\u00e0 CLB. HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp h\u00e0nh l\u00fd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra \u0111i v\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta t\u1eebng nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Mourinho. C\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 Conte b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Chelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng khao kh\u00e1t danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u1ed9t n\u0103m nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t m\u1edb h\u1ed7n \u0111\u1ed9n v\u00e0o n\u0103m ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nhan-2-tin-mung-truoc-tran-dau-voi-west-ham-172-183724.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/chelsea-nhan-2-tin-mung-truoc-tran-dau-voi-west-ham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nhan-2-tin-mung-truoc-tran-dau-voi-west-ham-172-183724.html\">Chelsea nh\u1eadn 2 tin m\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham, The Blues nh\u1eadn 2 tin vui khi Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Pedro \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ebd m\u1eb7t 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Stamford Bridge. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho Chelsea b\u1ecb top 4 b\u1ecf xa t\u1edbi 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby n\u1eefa v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi West Ham. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Conte t\u1ea1m th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng l\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 4 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Chelsea \u0111ang k\u00e9m Liverpool 11 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt h\u01a1n 2 tr\u1eadn. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng trong c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f9, The Blues s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m Liverpool v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m. H\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n trong tay m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Stamford Bridge v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 6/5. N\u1ebfu Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf Champions League, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Klopp m\u1ea5t th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o top 4 s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"880","checkdouble":"183750"},{"date":"20:59 07/04","title":"LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 20h45 ng\u00e0y 7/4 (VCK n\u1eef ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/7/link-xem-truc-tiep-nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-nhat-ban-20h45-ngay-74-vck-nu-chau-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.a