t{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 1 V-League di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m 5/4 v\u1eeba qua, HLV Marian Mihail \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Romania \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 1 V-League di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m 5/4 v\u1eeba qua, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, Marian Mihail \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi trong ng\u00e0y nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y t\u1eebng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mihail chia tay FLC Thanh Hoa Ly do HLV Mihail chia tay hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Mihail chia tay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a L\u00fd do HLV Mihail chia tay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/HLV-Mihail-chia-tay-FLC-Thanh-Hoa-Ly-do-HLV-Mihail-chia-tay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a chia tay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, HLV Mihail chia tay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y trong th\u1eddi gian qua, tuy nhi\u00ean nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u00e2u xa khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n V-League 2017 l\u00e0 v\u00ec \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo HLV Marian Mihail, c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i FLC Thanh Ho\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n bi\u1ebfn x\u1ea5u \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u. Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c r\u1eddi \u0111i. \u0110\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u1ee5 v\u01b0\u1ee3t r\u00e0o c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Sanna Kh\u00e1nh Ho\u00e0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c1 ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp cu\u1ed1i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m 5-6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 cho ph\u00e9p t\u1eeb ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. H\u1ecd mua \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n nhanh, u\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1ecdt d\u00f9 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 s\u1eafp v\u00e0o t\u1eadp\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cTrong v\u00f2ng 4 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3 qua, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng x\u1eed chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111ang l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i\u201d, HLV Mihail chia s\u1ebb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi HLV Mihail ra \u0111i, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf l\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i FLC Thanh Ho\u00e1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao v\u1ec1 cho tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Ho\u00e0ng Thanh T\u00f9ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nh\u1eafm 1 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u00f4ng H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"877","checkdouble":"183741"},{"date":"19:12 07/04","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/4: Real g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng cho Salah","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/6/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-74-real-gui-de-nghi-khung-cho-salah.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adC